<section
  class="grid grid-cols-14 gap-2 text-left grid-rows-2 md:p-5 lg:px-12 max-w-8xl mt-24 mb-24 md:mx-16 rounded-3xl z-30"
  aria-label="Proyectos y contenido destacado"
>
  <!-- Blog post section with semantic structure -->
  <article
    class="box-gen text-xl border-[1.5px] col-span-14 md:col-span-4 md:row-span-3"
    role="article"
    aria-labelledby="latest-post-title"
  >
    <div
      class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-9xl h-full rounded-[20px] border border-gray-400/20"
    >
      <header
        class="bg-black/60 w-fit px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-gray-400/20 mt-4 mx-4"
      >
        <span class="m-0 informative" role="banner">Último Post</span>
      </header>

      <aside class="w-max h-max border-l-2 my-2 mx-4 px-2" role="complementary">
        <time
          class="informative"
          datetime={new Date().toISOString()}
          aria-label={`Publicado el ${new Date().toLocaleDateString("es-ES", {
            day: "numeric",
            month: "long",
            year: "numeric",
          })}`}
        >
          {
            new Date().toLocaleDateString("es-ES", {
              day: "numeric",
              month: "long",
            })
          }
        </time>
      </aside>

      <main>
        <h3
          id="latest-post-title"
          class="font-static text-base m-3"
          role="heading"
          aria-level="3"
        >
          Aprendiendo a usar Grid y a usar estilos con Tailwind
        </h3>

        <section 
          id="Post" 
          class="mx-3 max-h-[350px] overflow-y-auto scrollbar-hidden" 
          aria-label="Resumen del post"
        >
          <p class="informative text-sm opacity-70 text-pretty pb-2">
            Me encanta lo fácil que es usar Grid con Tailwind. Recordar cómo
            hacerlo con CSS me cuesta aún más y tengo que echar un vistazo
            rápido para ver cómo posicionar celdas y darles su fracción a cada
            columna y fila. Aun así, lo que yo hago es a veces ayudarme del
            autocompletado y ver cómo funcionan los parámetros de <span
              class="font-bold text-blue-300"
              >grid-template-areas y grid-template-columns</span
            >. Aquí te dejo un muy buen recurso si quieres implementar un bento
            grid superfácil en tu proyecto.
            <a
              class="inline-block text-orange-400 underline text-xs font-static font-bold mt-2"
              href="https://cssgridgenerator.io/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">CSS grid generator</a
            >
          </p>
        </section>
        <footer class="mx-3 mb-3">
          <div class="flex items-center mt-2 gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="informative text-xs opacity-60">Categoría:</span>
            <mark
              class="bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs border border-blue-400/30"
            >
              Frontend
            </mark>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </main>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Scroll projects-->
  <article
    class="box-gen text-xl relative border col-span-14 md:col-span-5 h-80 md:block flex justify-center items-center"
  >
    <div
      class="bg-black/30 flex flex-col backdrop-blur-9xl h-full w-full rounded-[20px] border border-gray-400/20"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-black/60 w-fit px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-gray-400/30 mt-4 mx-4"
      >
        <span class="m-0 font-static informative">Proyectos Scroll</span>
      </div>
      <!-- embuelve proyectos  -->
      <div class="w-full h-full scale-95 mb-8 group relative">
        <div
          class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[80%] h-[85%] bg-pink-400 rounded-2xl -rotate-8 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:blur-sm"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[90%] h-[88%] bg-pink-100 rounded-2xl -rotate-4 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:blur-sm"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>
        <video
          autoplay
          muted
          loop
          class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-[90%] object-cover flex justify-center items-center rounded-[20px] transition-all duration-300 group-hover:blur-sm"
          aria-label="Video demostrativo de proyectos"
        >
          <source src="/imagenes/gta.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          Tu navegador no soporta el elemento video.
        </video>
        <a
          href="/projectos"
          class="font-static absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-fit flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 text-white text-center text-lg bg-black/60 px-4 py-2 rounded-2xl border border-gray-400/70 z-10 no-underline focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/50"
          aria-label="Ver todos los proyectos"
        >
          Ver proyectos
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
  <!--  Suitch project-->
  <article
    class="box-gen text-xl p-4 border col-span-14 md:col-span-5 h-80 md:block"
  >
    <a
      href="https://suitch.netlify.app/"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="block w-full h-full focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/50 rounded-[20px]"
      aria-label="Ver proyecto Suitch - Aplicación de streaming"
    >
      <img
        src="/imagenes/suitchweb.webp"
        alt="Captura de pantalla del proyecto Suitch, una aplicación de streaming similar a Twitch"
        class="w-full h-full object-fill flex justify-center items-center rounded-[20px]"
        width="320"
        height="240"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </a>
  </article>
  <div
    class="box-gen text-xl col-span-14 md:col-span-5 grid grid-rows-3 border border-gray-400/50"
  >
    <!-- sub-cuadros -->
    <div class="box-gen border p-2 m-1">
      <div
        class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-9xl h-full rounded-[20px] border border-gray-400/20"
      >
        sub cuadro 1
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="box-gen border p-2 m-1 row-span-3 shadow">
      <div
        class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-9xl h-full rounded-[20px] border border-gray-400/20"
      >
        sub cuadro 2
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- matera landing  -->
  <article
    class="box-gen rounde text-xl p-4 border col-span-14 md:col-span-5 h-80"
  >
    <div
      class="relative bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-9xl h-full rounded-[20px] border border-gray-400/20"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center mt-2">
        <div
          class="bg-black/60 relative w-fit px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-gray-400/30 mt-1 mx-4 f text-wrap"
        >
          <span class="m-0 font-static text-xs">Landing Page</span>
        </div>
        <span class="m-0 informative break-words text-wrap"
          >Restaurante-Menú</span
        >
      </div>
      <a
        href="https://www.lamatera.online/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="block focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/50 rounded-[20px]"
        aria-label="Ver sitio web de La Matera - Restaurante"
      >
        <img
          src="/imagenes/matera3.webp"
          alt="Captura de pantalla del sitio web de La Matera, una landing page para restaurante con menú digital"
          class="w-[94%] h-[74%] md:h-[76%] object-fill flex rounded-[20px] my-1 absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"
          width="300"
          height="200"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
  <div
    class="box-gen rounde text-xl p-4 border-2 col-span-14 md:col-span-10 hidden h-80"
  >
    <div
      class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-9xl h-full rounded-[20px] border border-gray-400/20"
    >
      cuarto cuadro
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  p {
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .informative {
    font-family: "static";
    font-size: 14px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* :is(.dark *) agregar esto al boxgen cuando hagamso el modo obscuro  */
  .box-gen {
    border-color: black;
    background-color: rgba(24, 24, 27, 0.2);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 6px 6px;
  }
